   122→  /**
   123→   * Creates the OpenAPI schema for the analyzed OWL class.
   124→   *
   125→   * <p>This method orchestrates the schema generation by:
   126→   * <ol>
   127→   *   <li>Initializing the base ObjectSchema with metadata</li>
   128→   *   <li>Creating a visitor to traverse class restrictions</li>
   129→   *   <li>Collecting relevant axioms from the ontology</li>
   130→   *   <li>Visiting axioms to gather property restrictions</li>
   131→   *   <li>Processing data, object, and taxonomy properties</li>
   132→   * </ol>
   133→   *
   134→   * @param analyzedClass the OWL class to generate a schema for
   135→   * @return the generated OpenAPI Schema object
